sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:modificationsToBackbone: BglII introduced to polylinker of pcDNA1/amp 3' of BamHI site.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:mutation: CFP(159-238) includes a substitution of His for Asn-164. GBeta-5 was amplified via PCR, which added an N-terminal linker sequence (RSIAT), a 5' BamHI site, and a 3' BglII site. Cloning into the BglII site of CFP(1-158) destroyed the BamHI site.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:aPortionOfThisPlasmidWasDerivedF: pECFP was purchased from Clontech. Beta-5 cDNA was obtained from Janet Robishaw, Weis Center for Research, Geisinger Clinic, Danville, PA.
